WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
On being a woman in corporate America,

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.200
the gender pay gap and more.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.800
I've been working in corporate for about 15 years now

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:15.300
and one thing I can tell you is that

00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:19.500
the pay gap is absolutely real.

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:24.100
I found out that my male colleague with less experience

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:28.700
was making 20% more than me for the same role.

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:33.200
And when I brought it up to HR, they said

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:37.800
"well, he negotiated better."

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:42.500
Ladies, always negotiate your salary.

00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:47.100
Know your worth and don't let anyone tell you otherwise.

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:51.600
This is something that affects all of us

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:56.200
and we need to keep having these conversations.
